---
title: Brilliant Beef and Caramelised Onion Puff Pie with Mash and Peas
description: Pie is one of the wonders of British cuisine - the combination of flaky puff pastry, rich sauce and tender fillings make a hearty meal that's loved by everyone in the family. This pie is inspired by the classic beef and onion pie, served with buttery mash and peas.
